 Army Corps of Engineers|Engineer]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 27th Engineer Bn Flash.png|<center>[[20th Engineer Brigade (United States)|20th Engineer Brigade's]] (ENG BDE) [[27th Engineer Battalion (United States)|27th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 57th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 57th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 161st Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 161st Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 6th Bde Eng Bn Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]] (IBCT) 6th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 127th Bde Engineer BN Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division]] (ABN DIV), 1st IBCT's 127th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 37th Eng BN Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[37th Engineer Battalion (United States)|37th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 738th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT, 37th Engineer Battalion's 738th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 307th Bde Eng BN Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 307th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 919th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT, 307th Engineer Battalion's 919th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 54th Brigade Engineer Battalion Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade]] [[Special Troops Battalion, 173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team (United States)|54th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Field Artillery Branch (United States)|Field Artillery]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 2nd Bn-377th Arty Reg Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]], [[377th Field Artillery Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:82nd Airborne Division Artillery Beret Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division Artillery]] (ABN DIV ARTY)</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's [[319th Field Artillery Regiment]], [[1st Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[2nd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[3rd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade's]] 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[4th Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|4th Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Infantry Branch (United States)|Infantry]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:75thrangerflash.svg|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]'s (USASOC) [[75th Ranger Regiment (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment]] and [[Special Troops Battalion]]</center>\nFile:1 Bn 75 Ranger Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>USASOC's [[1st Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5435.gif|<center>USASOC's [[2nd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5436.gif|<center>USASOC's [[3rd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th Bde-25th ID Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry (INF) Division's (DIV)]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team]] (IBCT)</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Bn-501st Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>25th INF DIV, 4th IBCT's [[501st Infantry Regiment (United States)|501st Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd Bn-509th Inf Reg Flash.png|<center>25th INF DIV, 4th IBCT's [[509th Infantry Regiment (United States)|509th Infantry Regiment]], 3rd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 82nd ABN DIV Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division|82nd Airborne (ABN) DIV]]</center>\nFile:504th Infantry Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 1st IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-501st PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's 501st Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt1BnFlash.PNG|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's [[504th Infantry Regiment (United States)|504th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:504InfRegt2BnFlash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 1st IBCT's 504th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-2nd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 2nd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[325th Infantry Regiment (United States)|325th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-325th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's 325th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[508th Infantry Regiment (United States)|508th Infantry Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army-82nd Airborne Division-3rd Brigade Combat Team-Beret Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV's 3rd IBCT</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's [[505th Infantry Regiment (United States)|505th Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-505th Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 505th Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-508th PIR Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 508th Infantry Regiment, 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 173rd ABN INF BCT Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 143rd ABN INF BN Flash.png|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's [[143rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|143rd Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's [[503rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|503rd Infantry Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd Airborne Brigade's 503rd Infantry Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Military Intelligence Corps (United States Army)|Military Intelligence]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army SFC MI BN Flash.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Command (Airborne)|1st Special Forces Command]]'s 389th Military Intelligence Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Military Police Corps (United States)|Military Police]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:16 MP Bde flash.png|<center>[[16th Military Police Brigade (United States)|16th Military Police (MP) Brigade (BDE)]]</center>\nFile:US Army 21st MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 21st MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 65th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 65th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 108th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 108th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 118th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 118th MP Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====Multidisciplinary Commands====\n<gallery>\nFile:JSOC flash.png|<center>[[Joint Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:USSOCOM flash.png|<center>[[United States Special Operations Command|Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCAFRICA flash.png|<center>[[United States African Command|Special Operations Command Africa]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCCENT flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Central]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCEUR flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Europe]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCKOR flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Korea]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCNORTH flash.png|<center>[[United States Northern Command|Special Operations Command North]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCPAC flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Pacific]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCSOUTH flash.svg|<center>[[United States Southern Command#Special Operations Command South|Special Operations Command South]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command (USACAPOC) beret flash.png|<center>[[United States Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command|US Army Civil Affairs and Psychological Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:USASOC flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]</center>\nFile:XVIII Airborne Corps BF.svg|<center>[[XVIII Airborne Corps]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Ordnance Corps (United States Army)|Ordnance]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:28 Ord Co beret flash.png|<center>[[52nd Ordnance Group (EOD)|52nd Ordnance Group]], 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 28th Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:722nd Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 722nd Ordnance Company</center>\nFile:767th Ordnance Co beret flash.png|<center>52nd Ordnance Group, 192nd Ordnance Battalion's 767th Ordnance Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Psychological operations (United States)|Psychological Operations]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 15th PSYOP BN Flash.png|<center>[[2nd Psychological Operations Group|2nd Psychological Operations (PSYOP) Group's]] 15th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US_Army_4th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[4th Psychological Operations Group|4th PSYOP Group]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 3rd PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 7th MISB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 7th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 8th MSIB Flash.png|<center>4th PSYOP Group's 8th PSYOP Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 301st Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>[[7th Psychological Operations Group|7th PSYOP Group]], 14th PSYOP Battalion's 301st Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 344th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 344th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 345th Tactical PSYOP Co Flash.png|<center>7th PSYOP Group, 17th PSYOP Battalion's 345th Tactical PSYOP Company</center>\nFile:US_Army_8th_Military_Information_Support_Group_Flash.png|<center>[[8th Psychological Operations Group|8th PSYOP Group]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Public affairs (military)|Public Affairs]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:Golden knights beret flash.gif|<center>[[United States Army Recruiting Command|Marketing and Engagement Brigade]]'s [[United States Army Parachute Team|US Army Parachute Team]]</center>\nFile:US Army 49th Public Affairs Detachment Flash.png|<center>82nd Airborne Division's 49th Public Affairs Detachment</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Quartermaster Corps (United States Army)|Quartermaster]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:Defense Logistics Agency-Defense Distribution Depot-Army Element Flash.png|<center>[[Defense Logistics Agency]]'s Defense Distribution Depot-Army Element</center>\nFile:US Army 647th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[3rd Sustainment Command (Expeditionary)|3rd Expeditionary Sustainment Command]], [[264th Combat Sustainment Support Battalion]]'s 647th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 294th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[Sustainment Brigades in the United States Army|36th Sustainment Brigade]]'s 294th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 36th Quartermaster Detachment Beret Flash.png|<center>36th Sustainment Brigade, 294th Quartermaster Company's 36th Quartermaster Detachment</center>\nFile:US Army 861st Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[77th Sustainment Brigade]]'s 861st Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 824th Quartermaster Company Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Sustainment Brigade]]'s 824th Quartermaster Company</center>\nFile:US Army 346th Quartermaster Company Flash.png|<center>[[518th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|518th Sustainment Brigade's]] 346th Quartermaster Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Signal Corps (United States Army)|Signal]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:USSOCOM-JSOC-JCU Beret Flash-Army Element.svg|<center>[[Joint Special Operations Command]]'s [[Joint Communications Unit]]\u2013Army element</center>\nFile:US Army 55st Signal Company Flash.png|<center>[[7th Signal Command (United States)|21st Signal Brigade's]] 55th Signal Company</center>\nFile:US Army 982nd Signal Company Flash.png|<center>[[335th Theater Signal Command (United States)|359th Signal Brigade's]] 982nd Signal Company</center>\nFile:US Army 112th SIG BN Flash.svg|<center>[[528th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|528th Sustainment Brigade's]] [[112th Special Operations Signal Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Special Forces (United States Army)|Special Forces]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 1st Special Forces Command-Joint Staff Element flash.svg|<center>Special Forces personnel assigned to the [[Joint Chiefs of Staff]]</center>\nFile:US Army Special Forces Personnel in non-Special Forces units flash.png|<center>Special Forces personnel in non-special operations units</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Special Forces Command Flash.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Command (Airborne)|1st Special Forces Command]]</center>\nFile:1sfg.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Group (United States)|1st Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:US Army 39th SFD Beret Flash.png|<center>1st Special Forces Group's 39th Special Forces Detachment</center>\nFile:3sfg.svg|<center>[[3rd Special Forces Group (United States)|3rd Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:5th SFG Beret Flash.png|<center>[[5th Special Forces Group (United States)|5th Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:7th Special Forces Group.svg|<center>[[7th Special Forces Group (United States)|7th Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:USA - 10th Special Forces Flash.svg|<center>[[10th Special Forces Group (United States)|10th Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:19sfg.png|<center>[[19th Special Forces Group (United States)|19th Special Forces Group]]</center>\nFile:20th Special Forces Group flash.png|<center>[[20th Special Forces Group (United States)|20th Special Forces Group]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====Support====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 725th Bde Support Bn Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]] [[725th Support Battalion (United States)|725th Brigade Support Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 307th Bde Support BN Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division]], 1st Infantry Brigade Combat Team's 307th Brigade Support Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 407th Bde Support BN Flash.svg|<center>82nd Airborne Division, 2nd Infantry Brigade Combat Team's [[407th Forward Support Battalion|407th Brigade Support Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 82nd Bde Support BN Flash.png|<center>82nd Airborne Division, 3rd Infantry Brigade Combat Team's [[82nd Brigade Support Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 122nd Aviation Support Bn Flash.svg|<center>82nd Airborne Division, Combat Aviation Brigade's 122nd Aviation Support Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 173rd Bde Support BN Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade's]] [[173rd Support Battalion (United States)|173rd Brigade Support Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Sustainment Brigades in the United States Army|Sustainment]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 82nd Sustainment Brigade Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Sustainment Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 528th Support Battalion Flash.png|<center>[[528th Sustainment Brigade (United States)|528th Sustainment Brigade (Special Operations)]]</center> \n</gallery>\